www.v2ex.com/t/1209676", "created": 1777535574, "deleted": 0, "content": "Windows\r\n\r\n需要的功能除了正常的 crud ，编辑表的时候能显示 alter 语句，最好支持数据迁移\r\n体验上来说不卡就行，能支持简单的自定义 ui\r\n\r\nnavicat 总是很卡，而且老是黑屏\r\ndbeaver 也卡，而且 ui 也不如 navicat 简洁\r\nBeekeeper 功能有点羸弱了，换字体都不行", "content_rendered": "<p>Windows</p>\n<p>需要的功能除了正常的 crud ，编辑表的时候能显示 alter 语句，最好支持数据迁移\n体验上来说不卡就行，能支持简单的自定义 ui</p>\n<p>navicat 总是很卡，而且老是黑屏\ndbeaver 也卡，而且 ui 也不如 navicat 简洁\nBeekeeper 功能有点羸弱了，换字体都不行</p>\n", "last_modified": 1777548109, "replies": 33, "id": 1209676}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_large.png?m=1775237570", "name": "claudecode", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_normal.png?m=1775237570", "title": "Claude Code", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claudecode", "topics": 232, "footer": "善语结善缘，恶语伤人心，勿发广告，会被删帖。", "header": "🤖 欢迎分享&讨论 [Claude Code]( https://claude.com) & Vibe Coding & AI 编程 等相关的话题。  \r\n🈲 发广告或引流内容会被删除", "title_alternative": "Claude Code", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1477/02db/1202_mini.png?m=1775237570", "stars": 303, "founder_id": 6746, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1202, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 3285, "username": "cxd8190102", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cxd8190102", "website": "", "twitter": "ontos474238", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "深圳", "tagline": "", "bio": "AI 文档解析工具：https://knowhereto.ai/\r\nAI 自动填表工具：https://www.gosnapfill.cn/landing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_mini.png?m=1775820080", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_normal.png?m=1775820080", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_large.png?m=1775820080", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xlarge.png?m=1775820080", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xxlarge.png?m=1775820080", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/72b3/8622/3285_xxxlarge.png?m=1775820080", "created": 1290895441, "last_modified": 1775820080, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zuosiruan", "last_touched": 1777573966, "title": "Anthropic 真是绝了，刚收完钱就把我踢了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1209737", "created": 1777548718, "deleted": 0, "content": "新人一个，还没用过 Claude ，之前有听说过它的恶名，但今天有需求，所以还是上去充了钱。\r\n\r\n结果！刚充完，它就把我踢下线了！我去！你拿钱的时候怎么不要求地域限制呢！\r\n\r\n之后就再也登不上去了。。。\r\n\r\n早上同事才在群里分享了一个新闻，说是美国有家做农业的公司，其中一个账号可能违规了，结果第二天一上班，整个团队的账号全部黑了，里面的东西直接没了，打电话也没人接。关键是，账号虽然没了，但消耗还继续，账户一直在扣钱！\r\n\r\n不得不说这个吃相实在是太难看了。\r\n\r\n现在很多公司都依赖 AI 干活吧，但 AI 公司也是越来越横行霸道了，说封禁你就封禁你，连声招呼也不打，里面多少公司的资产说没就没了，万一连个备份都没有，那损失真是亏麻了。\r\n\r\n而且还搞连坐制度，一人违规全司封号，没有预警没有提醒，你根本不知道是哪里出问题。\r\n\r\n真是太绝了，大家还是要保护好自己的数字资产啊。AI 使用安全也是安全问题。\r\n\r\nAnthropic 一生黑！", "content_rendered": "<p>新人一个，还没用过 Claude ，之前有听说过它的恶名，但今天有需求，所以还是上去充了钱。</p>\n<p>结果！刚充完，它就把我踢下线了！我去！你拿钱的时候怎么不要求地域限制呢！</p>\n<p>之后就再也登不上去了。。。</p>\n<p>早上同事才在群里分享了一个新闻，说是美国有家做农业的公司，其中一个账号可能违规了，结果第二天一上班，整个团队的账号全部黑了，里面的东西直接没了，打电话也没人接。关键是，账号虽然没了，但消耗还继续，账户一直在扣钱！</p>\n<p>不得不说这个吃相实在是太难看了。</p>\n<p>现在很多公司都依赖 AI 干活吧，但 AI 公司也是越来越横行霸道了，说封禁你就封禁你，连声招呼也不打，里面多少公司的资产说没就没了，万一连个备份都没有，那损失真是亏麻了。</p>\n<p>而且还搞连坐制度，一人违规全司封号，没有预警没有提醒，你根本不知道是哪里出问题。</p>\n<p>真是太绝了，大家还是要保护好自己的数字资产啊。AI 使用安全也是安全问题。</p>\n<p>Anthropic 一生黑！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1777589862, "replies": 32, "id": 1209737}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 70883, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9661, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 434592, "username": "lynn1su", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lynn1su", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_mini.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_normal.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_large.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xlarge.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxlarge.png?m=1734339081", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f59f/474b/434592_xxxlarge.png?m=1734339081", "created": 1565250257, "last_modified": 1734339081, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "chengYT", "last_touched": 1777555692, "title": "国家超算平台也出 coding plan 了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1209689", "created": 1777537845, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://i.imgur.com/VJQFQyf.png", "content_rendered": "<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/VJQFQyf.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VJQFQyf.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a>", "last_modified": 1777537845, "replies": 29, "id": 1209689}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "pronunciation", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "发音", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/pronunciation", "topics": 143, "footer": "", "header": "I'm sorry, I don't speak English.", "title_alternative": "", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 32, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 859, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 251820, "username": "fcoo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fcoo", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9239/6e05/251820_mini.png?m=1727356929", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9239/6e05/251820_normal.png?m=1727356929", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v